      <m:mn>6</m:mn>
    </m:msup>
    <m:mspace width="1em"/>
    <m:mrow>
          <m:mtext>Pascal</m:mtext>
    </m:mrow>
  </m:mrow>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-58">Similarly, mass of earth in scientific notation is :
</para>
<para id="element-59">
